title: website: tip.golang.org strange error
body:
by **blake.mizerany**: 
During a moment of temporary dyslexia or a Freudian slip, I typed this link into Chrome:

http://tip.golang.org/pkg/quick/testing/

I got:

vfs_tip: error statting "88b3b2fa4dde526bfbafc6aa30bac806323bc2c7" /
"src/pkg/quick/testing": vfs_tip: in
revStat("88b3b2fa4dde526bfbafc6aa30bac806323bc2c7",
"src/pkg/quick/testing"), failed to get parent "src/pkg/quick":
vfs_tip: error statting "88b3b2fa4dde526bfbafc6aa30bac806323bc2c7" /
"src/pkg/quick": file does not exist

o_O

-b
